      "updated": 1774016937554,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Skill: dubery-caption-gen/SKILL.md\n\nRules enforced:\n- 70% PRODUCT anchor / 30% PERSON anchor\n- Max 3 of same hook type per batch\n- 80% English / 20% Tagalog\n- Bundle offer (2 for P1,200) in at least 1 caption if N >= 5\n- CTA always last line\n\nOutput: 15 entries appended to .tmp/pipeline.json (status: APPROVED)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": "el_0011",
      "originalText": "Skill: dubery-caption-gen/SKILL.md\n\nRules enforced:\n- 70% PRODUCT anchor / 30% PERSON anchor\n- Max 3 of same hook type per batch\n- 80% English / 20% Tagalog\n- Bundle offer (2 for P1,200) in at least 1 caption if N >= 5\n- CTA always last line\n\nOutput: 15 entries appended to .tmp/pipeline.json (status: APPROVED)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
