      "updated": 1774016937554,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Skill: dubery-prompt-writer/SKILL.md\n\nPer caption:\n1. Caption Analysis (pain, relevance, proof, friction, type)\n2. Content Type Selection (A/B/C/D/E by visual_anchor)\n3. Headline = product model name (R1), NOT caption hook\n4. Build structured JSON prompt (scene, product, overlays)\n5. Self-check: 9 rules (R1-R9) verified before save\n\nOutput: .tmp/{id}_prompt_structured.json per caption\nNO product color/material descriptions anywhere (R2)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": "el_0019",
      "originalText": "Skill: dubery-prompt-writer/SKILL.md\n\nPer caption:\n1. Caption Analysis (pain, relevance, proof, friction, type)\n2. Content Type Selection (A/B/C/D/E by visual_anchor)\n3. Headline = product model name (R1), NOT caption hook\n4. Build structured JSON prompt (scene, product, overlays)\n5. Self-check: 9 rules (R1-R9) verified before save\n\nOutput: .tmp/{id}_prompt_structured.json per caption\nNO product color/material descriptions anywhere (R2)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
