      "updated": 1774016937554,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Skill: dubery-prompt-validator\n\nCheck categories:\n1. Product Fidelity (7)    2. Hero Treatment (2)\n3. Color Logic (2)         4. Overlays Complete (5)\n5. Overlays Duplicates (2) 6. Overlays Position (6)\n7. Logo Accuracy (3)\n\nVerdicts: PASS (proceed) | PATCH (fix inline, proceed) | REGENERATE (fail)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": "el_0027",
      "originalText": "Skill: dubery-prompt-validator\n\nCheck categories:\n1. Product Fidelity (7)    2. Hero Treatment (2)\n3. Color Logic (2)         4. Overlays Complete (5)\n5. Overlays Duplicates (2) 6. Overlays Position (6)\n7. Logo Accuracy (3)\n\nVerdicts: PASS (proceed) | PATCH (fix inline, proceed) | REGENERATE (fail)",
