      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774016937554,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Tool: python tools/pipeline/run_wf2.py --ids {id1} {id2} ...\n\nPer image:\n1. Submit to kie.ai createTask endpoint\n2. Poll recordInfo (90 retries x 4s = 6 min max)\n3. Download completed image to output/images/\n4. Backup to Google Drive\n5. Update pipeline.json status\n\nSequential to monitor each image landing before next gen starts",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": "el_0037",
      "originalText": "Tool: python tools/pipeline/run_wf2.py --ids {id1} {id2} ...\n\nPer image:\n1. Submit to kie.ai createTask endpoint\n2. Poll recordInfo (90 retries x 4s = 6 min max)\n3. Download completed image to output/images/\n4. Backup to Google Drive\n5. Update pipeline.json status\n\nSequential to monitor each image landing before next gen starts",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
