      "seed": 318032,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 960738,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774016937554,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Tool: python tools/meta_ads/stage_ad.py --id {id}\n\n- Loads/creates campaign + ad set from .tmp/ads_config.json\n- Creates one Ad per IMAGE_APPROVED caption\n- Budget: P200/day shared across all ads\n- Targeting: Philippines, 18-45, sunglasses/fashion/motorcycles\n- Ads created as PAUSED (RA activates manually in Ads Manager)\n- Meta Graph API v21.0",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": "el_0058",
      "originalText": "Tool: python tools/meta_ads/stage_ad.py --id {id}\n\n- Loads/creates campaign + ad set from .tmp/ads_config.json\n- Creates one Ad per IMAGE_APPROVED caption\n- Budget: P200/day shared across all ads\n- Targeting: Philippines, 18-45, sunglasses/fashion/motorcycles\n- Ads created as PAUSED (RA activates manually in Ads Manager)\n- Meta Graph API v21.0",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
