      "updated": 1774016937554,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "WAT Framework:  WORKFLOWS (.claude/skills/) define instructions  |  AGENT (Claude Code Opus) orchestrates  |  TOOLS (tools/*.py) execute\nFile locking via fcntl  |  .json.bak before every write  |  3 retries x 30s for transient API errors  |  Batch-aware re-scan for crash recovery",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "WAT Framework:  WORKFLOWS (.claude/skills/) define instructions  |  AGENT (Claude Code Opus) orchestrates  |  TOOLS (tools/*.py) execute\nFile locking via fcntl  |  .json.bak before every write  |  3 retries x 30s for transient API errors  |  Batch-aware re-scan for crash recovery",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
